disease_name: Congenital hypogonadotropic hypogonadism with cerebellar ataxia
Spinocerebellar ataxia (specifically those subtypes associated with hypogonadotropic hypogonadism)
Friedreich's ataxia (atypical presentation given the absence of spasticity and reflex hyperactivity)
Autosomal recessive spastic ataxia of Charlevoix-Saguenay (ARSACS)
